metadata.name: PRPRTY
metadata.description:
DAY 807
PNG / 3600x4200 / 300dpi / RGB

With 'PRPRTY' I decided to walk the line separating vulgarity & art.
The back of a cyberpunk woman, with a singular tatto.

“Property of Push” wants to open a window on woman objectification.
Trough mine I see incoherence.
Influencers actively fighting for gender equality and yet profiting trough self-objectification.

Nowadays, there is a prevailing sense of freedom to express oneself without boundaries. 
However, it begs the question: 
Are we truly free?
